why you need them for control</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"maintenance/#shutting-down-gracefully\">Shutting down gracefully</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"maintenance/#autoshutdown-script\">Autoshutdown script</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"maintenance/#network-port-redirector\">Network Port redirector</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"maintenance/#using-the-built-in-cron-system-for-periodically-running-commands\">Using the built-in cron system for periodically running commands</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"maintenance/#the-following-scripts-are-used-in-the-game-directory\">The following scripts are used in the game directory</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"maintenance/#textfiles-for-rhostmush\">Textfiles for RhostMUSH</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"troubleshooting/\">Troubleshooting</a><ul>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"troubleshooting/#stack-limit-and-debugging\">Stack limit and debugging</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"troubleshooting/#how-to-reset-the-password-for-1\">How to reset the password for #1</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"troubleshooting/#troubleshooting-difficulties-compiling-rhostmush\">Troubleshooting difficulties compiling RhostMUSH</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"troubleshooting/#dealing-with-db-corruption\">Dealing with DB Corruption</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l2\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"troubleshooting/#dealing-with-a-corrupt-mail-database\">Dealing with a corrupt mail database</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" hre